data.description: On a tree-lined street in the village of Arcanum, you'll find this darling 3 bed/1.5 bath blue 'dollhouse'. There's not much that can rival enjoying a cool evening on the welcoming front porch of this pristinely kept home. A front entry room boasts beautiful antique windows and serves as a dining room that connects to both the kitchen and living room. A generously sized living room will serve as a perfect place to unwind and relax. The bright kitchen is filled with sunlight and views into the back lawn. White kitchen cabinets offer loads of storage space to store appliances and cookware. A full bathroom off of the kitchen has a new walk-in tub. Additional tall cabinet storage, along with the furnace and water softener, can be found in the laundry room, which is conveniently just off of the kitchen. All three bedrooms can be found upstairs and feature plenty of closet space. A half bath is located in the largest of the three bedrooms. The back lawn is fenced and features green space, a mulched play area, and a partially covered patio area. Countless afternoons and evenings can be spent soaking up all that the yard offers. An impressive detached garage/barn serves as a handy workshop with separate parking spaces accessible by overhead doors. A courtyard at the side of the house is connected to the front and back lawn by an ornate white gate, which lends to this property's curb appeal. NEW ROOF in 2023 & WATER HEATER in 2022. This home could easily serve as the cover of a greeting card, it's simply a charmer. Schedule a tour with your agent today to see this Arcanum property.
